4551D01C.Line11.1343B7: I've seen your suffering at the hands of the Zakarum - the intolerance, the violence. I'm sorry your family couldn't be saved. But maybe others still can.

676E13AD.Line3.1343B7: I think so... but more importantly, I now have the knowledge I sought. Thank you, spirit, for showing us the truth.

B7A43F7A.VoiceDir3.1343B7: Dazed and recovering from being possessed, but grateful for learning what he did through the spirit's possession.

F0F910F3.Line9.1343B7: Thank you both. I will take what I've learned here to the Cathedral of Light. I hope I'm not too late.
